summary: This document is a summary of account balances and transactions for a Deutsche Bank account over the month of August 2018. It details various debits and credits, including payroll deductions and other transactions, providing insight into the financial activities associated with the account.
keyFacts: The account had a beginning balance of $817,463.61 on August 1, 2018.
The account experienced various debits including payroll fees and health premiums totaling significant amounts.
The ending balance as of August 31, 2018, was $594,666.62.
Multiple preauthorized debits were made throughout the month for various services and payments.
The document includes instructions for reporting errors related to electronic and non-electronic funds transfers.
